  "title": "",
  "body": " Juicee hot dogs come in packages of 10, and Juicee hot dog buns come in packages of 8. How many packages of each should you buy so that you won't have any hot dogs or buns left over?  What is the LCM of 8 and 10?   4 packages of hot dogs and 5 packages of buns  40  "
